<paragraph blockId="70.[667,1194,817,1759]" lastBlockId="71.[701,1228,1647,1759]" lastPageId="71" lastPageNumber="71" pageId="70" pageNumber="70">Body bicolored. Head and pronotum black; elytra reddish brown; abdominal segments III to V reddish brown with darker infusions basally; segments VI to VIII dark reddish brown with paler reddish-brown infusions. Legs bicolored, pale reddish brown to yellowish brown with dark reddish brown femorotibial spot.</paragraph>
